data.title: Episode 2567 (11 August 2003)
data.meta_description: Billy's gutted to realise that he's been fleeced. Little Mo gets excited about the future. Meanwhile, Ronnie invites Zoe to the wedding. Billy Mitchell - Perry Fenwick 'Little' Mo Mitchell - Kacey Ainsworth Janine Butcher - Charlie Brooks Barry Evans - Charlie Brooks Paul Trueman - Gary Beadle...
data.text:
Billy still doesn't know how to tell Little Mo that he's lost a lot of their money.

Barry has been looking after Natalie and Jack whilst they've been ill, they seem to be getting on well which is bad news for Janine and Paul's plan.

Dot is still intent on giving up her job at the laundrette, but Sonia, Jim and Pauline aren't happy about it.

Adi has been lying to Dan about having a girlfriend and Kareena isn't happy about it and wants him to come clean. Instead, Adi asks Sasha to come to the wedding with him and pose as his girlfriend.

Martin is growing marijuana plants in the garden shed.
